{"tid":1609442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日開始 無限期罷工","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T03:54:09.000Z","uid":122827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13406ac3bb10a3f69548c746adf2272040d2a81e","tid":1609442,"uid":122827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"唔好話咩冇文宣冇人參與 從來都只係差你一個<br />\n唔好話成效唔大就唔參與 從來都係因為唔夠多人罷先唔成功<br />\n由612 721 831到今日 衝既衝塞既塞 出埋黑社會同玩批鬥 到今時今日政府依然故我<br />\n你有冇諗過問題在於你地呢班搵盡藉口<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔參與癱瘓社會</span></span>既人<br />\n<br />\n政府同黑警冇當過大家係人 你做衝衝子又好和理非都好 佢地都係收份糧然後每日大魚大肉<br />\n而你就算平日返工放假抗爭都唔會有咁既生活 每日仲要驚比人篤灰比人拉<br />\n你真係願意為呢個社會 呢間只要唔返工就炒你既公司賣命?<br />\n<br />\n你話冇文宣冇人罷所以唔罷 而家我咪同你講左 你係咪會一齊罷先?<br />\n你話冇人參與所以唔罷 咁冇第一個人參與係咪所有人都唔洗參與?<br />\n你話冇左份工係咪我養你同屋企人 我同你講 今日保得住你份工聽日你條命凍過水<br />\n<br />\n如果大家係因為今次運動失業/經濟有壓力 歡迎大家圍個爐<br />\n香港人除左錢多冇野多 如果眾籌一筆錢確保大家基本生活可以令你敢於對抗呢個社會 我可以捐哂全副身家出黎<br />\n<br />\n如果唔甘心成為呢個社會既奴隸 唔甘心成為支共極權統治下既家畜<br />\n由今日開始 行出你既第一步"},{"pid":"ccd6d57acc322901eda9caed551dac911bee0e60","tid":1609442,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1609038/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1609038/page/1</a><br />\n九龍塘九龍塘九龍塘九龍塘"},{"pid":"a5b411e3de792c0a4a96fe71deff81b6d02550f6","tid":1609442,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MoZErGD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoZErGD.jpg&h=1eb5cca5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQcuOUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQcuOUZ.jpg&h=1bbf000c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCmvymE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCmvymE.jpg&h=3be05987&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N95oTmE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN95oTmE.jpg&h=6c785ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZ2iHe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZ2iHe0.jpg&h=ef8d796e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ff13bfc06ffea2d54266de0e1411138d698c752","tid":1609442,"uid":122827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今天不出來<br />\n明天出不來</span></span>"},{"pid":"9751ccf72006769ce20af363b816ab0e7ecd9b05","tid":1609442,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"香港人係唔會做"}]}